Battleship! C++ Console Game
w/ Online Multiplayer

Game by Terrance Coyle
All Rights Reserved
Feel free to use for personal reasons

Server is based off an online tutorial and modified for turn based use - feel free to use for whatever you wish.

Compile both.
Run server with chosen port (ie: ./server <port>)
Run game on 2 different machines (ie: ./battleship <ip or host name> <port>)

Game will automatically wait for a match from the server.
Once matchmake is complete, game begins.

Have fun and enjoy. It will be updated.